summary: This is a brief email chain from December 23, 2020, discussing the impending expiration of a seal on a 'triggerfish' warrant related to Ghislaine Maxwell. The correspondence involves a query about whether the seal needs to be extended or can be allowed to lapse.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The 'triggerfish' warrant mentioned in the email subject and body is related to her.

events.title: Email regarding Triggerfish Warrant Seal
events.description: An email exchange occurs regarding the seal on a 'triggerfish' warrant related to Ghislaine Maxwell, which is set to expire soon. The sender inquires if the seal needs to be extended or can be allowed to lapse.

keyFacts: A 'triggerfish' warrant related to Ghislaine Maxwell was under seal and set to expire around December 23, 2020.
Legal personnel were corresponding about whether to extend the seal on this warrant or let it lapse.
The document is a brief internal email chain, indicating ongoing legal monitoring or procedures concerning Maxwell at that date.
